                        <body><div class="ds-markdown ds-markdown--block" style="--ds-md-zoom: 1.143; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph">基于每德科技案例和提升学习规划效率的需求，我为您设计了一个“企业学习规划智能支持系统”框架，重点解决顾问效率与输出质量问题：</p><h3>系统核心架构</h3><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong>1. 智能诊断引擎（提效关键）</strong></p><ul><li>痛点：顾问需从零分析企业录音/文本</li><li>解决方案：<ul><li>上传会议录音 → 自动转写+关键词提取（如文中“品牌能力弱”“抖音机会”“关键人才缺口”）</li><li>生成<strong>三维诊断报告</strong>：<div class="md-code-block md-code-block-dark"><style>.kvfysmfp{overflow:hidden;touch-action:none}.ufhsfnkm{transform-origin: 0 0}</style><div class="kvfysmfp _6213ab4"><svg role="graphics-document document" viewBox="0 0 1206.390625 174" class="flowchart mermaid-svg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100%" id="mermaid-svg-15" style="max-width: 1206.39px; transform-origin: 0px 0px; user-select: none; transform: translate(0px, 49.7265px) scale(0.999999);"><style>#mermaid-svg-15{font-family:"trebuchet ms",verdana,arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;fill:#ccc;}@keyframes edge-animation-frame{from{stroke-dashoffset:0;}}@keyframes dash{to{stroke-dashoffset:0;}}#mermaid-svg-15 .edge-animation-slow{stroke-dasharray:9,5!important;stroke-dashoffset:900;animation:dash 50s linear infinite;stroke-linecap:round;}#mermaid-svg-15 .edge-animation-fast{stroke-dasharray:9,5!important;stroke-dashoffset:900;animation:dash 20s linear infinite;stroke-linecap:round;}#mermaid-svg-15 .error-icon{fill:#a44141;}#mermaid-svg-15 .error-text{fill:#ddd;stroke:#ddd;}#mermaid-svg-15 .edge-thickness-normal{stroke-width:1px;}#mermaid-svg-15 .edge-thickness-thick{stroke-width:3.5px;}#mermaid-svg-15 .edge-pattern-solid{stroke-dasharray:0;}#mermaid-svg-15 .edge-thickness-invisible{stroke-width:0;fill:none;}#mermaid-svg-15 .edge-pattern-dashed{stroke-dasharray:3;}#mermaid-svg-15 .edge-pattern-dotted{stroke-dasharray:2;}#mermaid-svg-15 .marker{fill:lightgrey;stroke:lightgrey;}#mermaid-svg-15 .marker.cross{stroke:lightgrey;}#mermaid-svg-15 svg{font-family:"trebuchet ms",verdana,arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;}#mermaid-svg-15 p{margin:0;}#mermaid-svg-15 .label{font-family:"trebuchet ms",verdana,arial,sans-serif;color:#ccc;}#mermaid-svg-15 .cluster-label text{fill:#F9FFFE;}#mermaid-svg-15 .cluster-label span{color:#F9FFFE;}#mermaid-svg-15 .cluster-label span p{background-color:transparent;}#mermaid-svg-15 .label text,#mermaid-svg-15 span{fill:#ccc;color:#ccc;}#mermaid-svg-15 .node rect,#mermaid-svg-15 .node circle,#mermaid-svg-15 .node ellipse,#mermaid-svg-15 .node polygon,#mermaid-svg-15 .node path{fill:#1f2020;stroke:#ccc;stroke-width:1px;}#mermaid-svg-15 .rough-node .label text,#mermaid-svg-15 .node .label text,#mermaid-svg-15 .image-shape .label,#mermaid-svg-15 .icon-shape .label{text-anchor:middle;}#mermaid-svg-15 .node .katex path{fill:#000;stroke:#000;stroke-width:1px;}#mermaid-svg-15 .rough-node .label,#mermaid-svg-15 .node .label,#mermaid-svg-15 .image-shape .label,#mermaid-svg-15 .icon-shape .label{text-align:center;}#mermaid-svg-15 .node.clickable{cursor:pointer;}#mermaid-svg-15 .root .anchor path{fill:lightgrey!important;stroke-width:0;stroke:lightgrey;}#mermaid-svg-15 .arrowheadPath{fill:lightgrey;}#mermaid-svg-15 .edgePath .path{stroke:lightgrey;stroke-width:2.0px;}#mermaid-svg-15 .flowchart-link{stroke:lightgrey;fill:none;}#mermaid-svg-15 .edgeLabel{background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 34.4117647059%);text-align:center;}#mermaid-svg-15 .edgeLabel p{background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 34.4117647059%);}#mermaid-svg-15 .edgeLabel rect{opacity:0.5;background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 34.4117647059%);fill:hsl(0, 0%, 34.4117647059%);}#mermaid-svg-15 .labelBkg{background-color:rgba(87.75, 87.75, 87.75, 0.5);}#mermaid-svg-15 .cluster rect{fill:hsl(180, 1.5873015873%, 28.3529411765%);stroke:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);stroke-width:1px;}#mermaid-svg-15 .cluster text{fill:#F9FFFE;}#mermaid-svg-15 .cluster span{color:#F9FFFE;}#mermaid-svg-15 div.mermaidTooltip{position:absolute;text-align:center;max-width:200px;padding:2px;font-family:"trebuchet ms",verdana,arial,sans-serif;font-size:12px;background:hsl(20, 1.5873015873%, 12.3529411765%);border:1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);border-radius:2px;pointer-events:none;z-index:100;}#mermaid-svg-15 .flowchartTitleText{text-anchor:middle;font-size:18px;fill:#ccc;}#mermaid-svg-15 rect.text{fill:none;stroke-width:0;}#mermaid-svg-15 .icon-shape,#mermaid-svg-15 .image-shape{background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 34.4117647059%);text-align:center;}#mermaid-svg-15 .icon-shape p,#mermaid-svg-15 .image-shape p{background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 34.4117647059%);padding:2px;}#mermaid-svg-15 .icon-shape rect,#mermaid-svg-15 .image-shape rect{opacity:0.5;background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 34.4117647059%);fill:hsl(0, 0%, 34.4117647059%);}#mermaid-svg-15 :root{--mermaid-font-family:"trebuchet ms",verdana,arial,sans-serif;}</style><g><marker orient="auto" markerHeight="8" markerWidth="8" markerUnits="userSpaceOnUse" refY="5" refX="5" viewBox="0 0 10 10" class="marker flowchart-v2" id="mermaid-svg-15_flowchart-v2-pointEnd"><path style="stroke-width: 1; stroke-dasharray: 1, 0;" class="arrowMarkerPath" d="M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z"></path></marker><marker orient="auto" markerHeight="8" markerWidth="8" markerUnits="userSpaceOnUse" refY="5" refX="4.5" viewBox="0 0 10 10" class="marker flowchart-v2" id="mermaid-svg-15_flowchart-v2-pointStart"><path style="stroke-width: 1; stroke-dasharray: 1, 0;" class="arrowMarkerPath" d="M 0 5 L 10 10 L 10 0 z"></path></marker><marker orient="auto" markerHeight="11" markerWidth="11" markerUnits="userSpaceOnUse" refY="5" refX="11" viewBox="0 0 10 10" class="marker flowchart-v2" id="mermaid-svg-15_flowchart-v2-circleEnd"><circle style="stroke-width: 1; stroke-dasharray: 1, 0;" class="arrowMarkerPath" r="5" cy="5" cx="5"></circle></marker><marker orient="auto" markerHeight="11" markerWidth="11" markerUnits="userSpaceOnUse" refY="5" refX="-1" viewBox="0 0 10 10" class="marker flowchart-v2" id="mermaid-svg-15_flowchart-v2-circleStart"><circle style="stroke-width: 1; stroke-dasharray: 1, 0;" class="arrowMarkerPath" r="5" cy="5" cx="5"></circle></marker><marker orient="auto" markerHeight="11" markerWidth="11" markerUnits="userSpaceOnUse" refY="5.2" refX="12" viewBox="0 0 11 11" class="marker cross flowchart-v2" id="mermaid-svg-15_flowchart-v2-crossEnd"><path style="stroke-width: 2; stroke-dasharray: 1, 0;" class="arrowMarkerPath" d="M 1,1 l 9,9 M 10,1 l -9,9"></path></marker><marker orient="auto" markerHeight="11" markerWidth="11" markerUnits="userSpaceOnUse" refY="5.2" refX="-1" viewBox="0 0 11 11" class="marker cross flowchart-v2" id="mermaid-svg-15_flowchart-v2-crossStart"><path style="stroke-width: 2; stroke-dasharray: 1, 0;" class="arrowMarkerPath" d="M 1,1 l 9,9 M 10,1 l -9,9"></path></marker><g class="root"><g class="clusters"></g><g class="edgePaths"><path marker-end="url(#mermaid-svg-15_flowchart-v2-pointEnd)" style="" class="edge-thickness-normal edge-pattern-solid edge-thickness-normal edge-pattern-solid flowchart-link" id="L_A_A1_0" d="M118.511,62L111.292,66.167C104.073,70.333,89.634,78.667,82.415,86.333C75.195,94,75.195,101,75.195,104.5L75.195,108"></path><path marker-end="url(#mermaid-svg-15_flowchart-v2-pointEnd)" style="" class="edge-thickness-normal edge-pattern-solid edge-thickness-normal edge-pattern-solid flowchart-link" id="L_A_A2_0" d="M212.074,62L219.294,66.167C226.513,70.333,240.952,78.667,248.171,86.333C255.391,94,255.391,101,255.391,104.5L255.391,108"></path><path marker-end="url(#mermaid-svg-15_flowchart-v2-pointEnd)" style="" class="edge-thickness-normal edge-pattern-solid edge-thickness-normal edge-pattern-solid flowchart-link" id="L_B_B1_0" d="M497.391,57.389L483.724,62.324C470.057,67.259,442.724,77.13,429.057,85.565C415.391,94,415.391,101,415.391,104.5L415.391,108"></path><path marker-end="url(#mermaid-svg-15_flowchart-v2-pointEnd)" style="" class="edge-thickness-normal edge-pattern-solid edge-thickness-normal edge-pattern-solid flowchart-link" id="L_B_B2_0" d="M559.391,62L559.391,66.167C559.391,70.333,559.391,78.667,559.391,86.333C559.391,94,559.391,101,559.391,104.5L559.391,108"></path><path marker-end="url(#mermaid-svg-15_flowchart-v2-pointEnd)" style="" class="edge-thickness-normal edge-pattern-solid edge-thickness-normal edge-pattern-solid flowchart-link" id="L_B_B3_0" d="M621.391,56.211L636.391,61.342C651.391,66.474,681.391,76.737,696.391,85.368C711.391,94,711.391,101,711.391,104.5L711.391,108"></path><path marker-end="url(#mermaid-svg-15_flowchart-v2-pointEnd)" style="" class="edge-thickness-normal edge-pattern-solid edge-thickness-normal edge-pattern-solid flowchart-link" id="L_C_C1_0" d="M945.391,57.389L931.724,62.324C918.057,67.259,890.724,77.13,877.057,85.565C863.391,94,863.391,101,863.391,104.5L863.391,108"></path><path marker-end="url(#mermaid-svg-15_flowchart-v2-pointEnd)" style="" class="edge-thickness-normal edge-pattern-solid edge-thickness-normal edge-pattern-solid flowchart-link" id="L_C_C2_0" d="M1007.391,62L1007.391,66.167C1007.391,70.333,1007.391,78.667,1007.391,86.333C1007.391,94,1007.391,101,1007.391,104.5L1007.391,108"></path><path marker-end="url(#mermaid-svg-15_flowchart-v2-pointEnd)" style="" class="edge-thickness-normal edge-pattern-solid edge-thickness-normal edge-pattern-solid flowchart-link" id="L_C_C3_0" d="M1069.391,57.389L1083.057,62.324C1096.724,67.259,1124.057,77.13,1137.724,85.565C1151.391,94,1151.391,101,1151.391,104.5L1151.391,108"></path></g><g class="edgeLabels"><g class="edgeLabel"><g transform="translate(0, 0)" class="label"><foreignObject height="0" width="0"><div style="display: table-cell; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;" class="labelBkg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="edgeLabel"></span></div></foreignObject></g></g><g class="edgeLabel"><g transform="translate(0, 0)" class="label"><foreignObject height="0" width="0"><div style="display: table-cell; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;" class="labelBkg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="edgeLabel"></span></div></foreignObject></g></g><g class="edgeLabel"><g transform="translate(0, 0)" class="label"><foreignObject height="0" width="0"><div style="display: table-cell; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;" class="labelBkg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="edgeLabel"></span></div></foreignObject></g></g><g class="edgeLabel"><g transform="translate(0, 0)" class="label"><foreignObject height="0" width="0"><div style="display: table-cell; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;" class="labelBkg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="edgeLabel"></span></div></foreignObject></g></g><g class="edgeLabel"><g transform="translate(0, 0)" class="label"><foreignObject height="0" width="0"><div style="display: table-cell; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;" class="labelBkg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="edgeLabel"></span></div></foreignObject></g></g><g class="edgeLabel"><g transform="translate(0, 0)" class="label"><foreignObject height="0" width="0"><div style="display: table-cell; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;" class="labelBkg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="edgeLabel"></span></div></foreignObject></g></g><g class="edgeLabel"><g transform="translate(0, 0)" class="label"><foreignObject height="0" width="0"><div style="display: table-cell; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;" class="labelBkg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="edgeLabel"></span></div></foreignObject></g></g><g class="edgeLabel"><g transform="translate(0, 0)" class="label"><foreignObject height="0" width="0"><div style="display: table-cell; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;" class="labelBkg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="edgeLabel"></span></div></foreignObject></g></g></g><g class="nodes"><g transform="translate(165.29296875, 35)" id="flowchart-A-0" class="node default"><rect height="54" width="124" y="-27" x="-62" style="" class="basic label-container"></rect><g transform="translate(-32, -12)" style="" class="label"><rect></rect><foreignObject height="24" width="64"><div style="display: table-cell; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="nodeLabel">经营机会</span></div></foreignObject></g></g><g transform="translate(75.1953125, 139)" id="flowchart-A1-1" class="node default"><rect height="54" width="134.390625" y="-27" x="-67.1953125" ry="5" rx="5" style="" class="basic label-container"></rect><g transform="translate(-52.1953125, -12)" style="" class="label"><rect></rect><foreignObject height="24" width="104.390625"><div style="display: table-cell; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="nodeLabel">抖音/海外红利</span></div></foreignObject></g></g><g transform="translate(255.390625, 139)" id="flowchart-A2-3" class="node default"><rect height="54" width="126" y="-27" x="-63" ry="5" rx="5" style="" class="basic label-container"></rect><g transform="translate(-48, -12)" style="" class="label"><rect></rect><foreignObject height="24" width="96"><div style="display: table-cell; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="nodeLabel">小红书未开发</span></div></foreignObject></g></g><g transform="translate(559.390625, 35)" id="flowchart-B-4" class="node default"><rect height="54" width="124" y="-27" x="-62" style="" class="basic label-container"></rect><g transform="translate(-32, -12)" style="" class="label"><rect></rect><foreignObject height="24" width="64"><div style="display: table-cell; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="nodeLabel">能力短板</span></div></foreignObject></g></g><g transform="translate(415.390625, 139)" id="flowchart-B1-5" class="node default"><rect height="54" width="94" y="-27" x="-47" ry="5" rx="5" style="" class="basic label-container"></rect><g transform="translate(-32, -12)" style="" class="label"><rect></rect><foreignObject height="24" width="64"><div style="display: table-cell; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="nodeLabel">品牌营销</span></div></foreignObject></g></g><g transform="translate(559.390625, 139)" id="flowchart-B2-7" class="node default"><rect height="54" width="94" y="-27" x="-47" ry="5" rx="5" style="" class="basic label-container"></rect><g transform="translate(-32, -12)" style="" class="label"><rect></rect><foreignObject height="24" width="64"><div style="display: table-cell; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="nodeLabel">产品定义</span></div></foreignObject></g></g><g transform="translate(711.390625, 139)" id="flowchart-B3-9" class="node default"><rect height="54" width="110" y="-27" x="-55" ry="5" rx="5" style="" class="basic label-container"></rect><g transform="translate(-40, -12)" style="" class="label"><rect></rect><foreignObject height="24" width="80"><div style="display: table-cell; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="nodeLabel">跨部门协同</span></div></foreignObject></g></g><g transform="translate(1007.390625, 35)" id="flowchart-C-10" class="node default"><rect height="54" width="124" y="-27" x="-62" style="" class="basic label-container"></rect><g transform="translate(-32, -12)" style="" class="label"><rect></rect><foreignObject height="24" width="64"><div style="display: table-cell; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="nodeLabel">管理基础</span></div></foreignObject></g></g><g transform="translate(863.390625, 139)" id="flowchart-C1-11" class="node default"><rect height="54" width="94" y="-27" x="-47" ry="5" rx="5" style="" class="basic label-container"></rect><g transform="translate(-32, -12)" style="" class="label"><rect></rect><foreignObject height="24" width="64"><div style="display: table-cell; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="nodeLabel">目标缺失</span></div></foreignObject></g></g><g transform="translate(1007.390625, 139)" id="flowchart-C2-13" class="node default"><rect height="54" width="94" y="-27" x="-47" ry="5" rx="5" style="" class="basic label-container"></rect><g transform="translate(-32, -12)" style="" class="label"><rect></rect><foreignObject height="24" width="64"><div style="display: table-cell; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="nodeLabel">绩效粗放</span></div></foreignObject></g></g><g transform="translate(1151.390625, 139)" id="flowchart-C3-15" class="node default"><rect height="54" width="94" y="-27" x="-47" ry="5" rx="5" style="" class="basic label-container"></rect><g transform="translate(-32, -12)" style="" class="label"><rect></rect><foreignObject height="24" width="64"><div style="display: table-cell; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="nodeLabel">流程空白</span></div></foreignObject></g></g></g></g></g></svg></div></div></li></ul></li></ul><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong>2. 策略匹配库（质量保障）</strong></p><ul><li>动态知识图谱：<ul><li>关联案例策略（如文中“华宝新能源外挂顾问”“南河合伙制”）</li><li>智能推荐方案：<div class="md-code-block md-code-block-dark"><pre>[每德需求] 品牌能力建设 → 
[匹配方案] 分阶段实施：
阶段1：刀哥团队国内陪跑（0-6个月）
阶段2：搭建内容中台（6-12个月）
阶段3：GTM体系（张磊课程）</pre></div></li></ul></li></ul><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong>3. 资源连接器</strong></p><ul><li>智能师资匹配：<div class="md-code-block md-code-block-dark"><pre><span class="token comment"># 伪代码示例</span>
<span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">match_teacher</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>enterprise_type<span class="token punctuation">,</span> stage<span class="token punctuation">,</span> pain_point<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>
  <span class="token keyword">if</span> enterprise_type <span class="token operator">==</span> <span class="token string">"消费品牌"</span> <span class="token keyword">and</span> pain_point <span class="token operator">==</span> <span class="token string">"品效合一"</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>
      <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token string">"徐薇"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token string">"李科"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token string">"刀哥团队"</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span> 
  <span class="token keyword">elif</span> stage <span class="token operator">==</span> <span class="token string">"0-1扩张"</span> <span class="token keyword">and</span> pain_point <span class="token operator">==</span> <span class="token string">"关键人才"</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>
      <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token string">"张磊（战略级挖猎）"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token string">"川老师（实操陪跑）"</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span></pre></div></li></ul><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong>4. 实施路线图生成</strong></p><ul><li>自动输出带风险提示的规划：<blockquote><strong>关键风险预警</strong>：<ul><li>品牌建设需12个月见效，与抖音红利期存在时间冲突</li><li>空降高管失败率＞50%（见历史案例库No.CT203）</li></ul></blockquote></li></ul><h3>提升效率的3大创新点</h3><ol start="1"><li><strong>对话洞察强化</strong><ul><li>自动标记决策节点（如文中“先经营后管理”原则）</li><li>识别未明需求（例：检测到7次“组织”讨论但0次具体动作 → 提示避免过早体系化）</li></ul></li><li><strong>动态知识沉淀</strong><ul><li>顾问新增方案自动生成「策略卡片」：<div class="md-code-block md-code-block-dark"><pre>[策略ID] M03-2025 
[场景] 百人企业快速扩张期 
[核心] 外挂顾问+内部委员会过渡机制 
[来源] 每德科技案例（2025.06）</pre></div></li></ul></li><li><strong>质量校验系统</strong><ul><li>方案完整性检查（必含项：机会窗口期/能力建设路径/资源投入ROI）</li><li>冲突检测（例：当同时选择“强绩效导向”+“创意型团队”时触发警告）</li></ul></li></ol><h3>系统操作流程</h3><div class="md-code-block md-code-block-dark"><pre><span class="token keyword">sequenceDiagram</span>
   顾问<span class="token arrow operator">-&gt;&gt;</span>+系统： 上传访谈录音/文本
   系统<span class="token arrow operator">--&gt;&gt;</span>-AI引擎： 自动提取关键词
   AI引擎<span class="token arrow operator">--&gt;&gt;</span>知识库： 匹配相似案例
   知识库<span class="token arrow operator">--&gt;&gt;</span>-系统： 返回策略包
   系统<span class="token arrow operator">-&gt;&gt;</span>顾问： 生成诊断报告+方案草案
   顾问<span class="token arrow operator">-&gt;&gt;</span>系统： 调整方案细节
   系统<span class="token arrow operator">-&gt;&gt;</span>企业端： 输出可视化路线图</pre></div><h3>预期效果</h3><div class="markdown-table-wrapper"><table><thead><tr><th>指标</th><th>当前状态</th><th>系统上线目标</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>方案产出时间</td><td>3-5天/企业</td><td>≤4小时</td></tr><tr><td>关键策略遗漏</td><td>平均2.3项/案</td><td>0项</td></tr><tr><td>资源匹配精度</td><td>依赖个人经验</td><td>90%+推荐准确率</td></tr></tbody></table></div><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong>实施建议</strong>：首期聚焦「消费企业增长期」场景开发，复用每德案例中的策略逻辑（先抓红利→补关键人→缓建体系），后续扩展制造业/科技企业模块。系统命名为<strong>PathFinder智航系统</strong>（中：智航企业学习规划平台），体现“智能导航+业务领航”双重价值。</p></div></body>
                    </html>